fields.name: Basil
fields.description: A versatile and aromatic herb, perfect for adding flavor to your favorite dishes. Basil is easy to grow and thrives in balcony containers.

fields.name: Cherry Tomato
fields.description: Compact and productive, cherry tomato plants are ideal for balcony gardens. Enjoy fresh tomatoes throughout the summer.

fields.name: Strawberry
fields.description: Sweet and juicy strawberries right from your balcony. These plants are easy to grow and provide delicious fruit.

fields.name: Lavender
fields.description: Lavender adds a beautiful fragrance and color to your balcony. It is also known for its calming properties.

fields.name: Mint
fields.description: Mint is perfect for adding a refreshing flavor to drinks and dishes. It grows vigorously in containers on a balcony.

fields.name: Rosemary
fields.description: An essential herb for any home cook, rosemary is easy to grow and adds a wonderful flavor to a variety of dishes.

fields.name: Organic Potting Soil
fields.description: High-quality organic potting soil, perfect for all your container gardening needs. Enriched with nutrients to support healthy plant growth.

fields.name: All-Purpose Fertilizer
fields.description: Balanced all-purpose fertilizer suitable for a wide range of plants. Promotes vigorous growth and blooming.

fields.name: Compost
fields.description: Rich, organic compost to improve soil structure and provide essential nutrients for plants. Perfect for gardens and containers.

fields.name: Garden Shovel Set
fields.description: Durable garden shovel with a comfortable grip, ideal for digging and planting. Made from high-quality steel. Set of 3.

fields.name: Pruning Shears
fields.description: Sharp and precise pruning shears for trimming plants and shrubs. Ergonomic handle for comfortable use.

fields.name: Watering Can
fields.description: Stylish and functional watering can with a long spout for easy watering. Holds up to 2 liters of water.
